OL,3,EPREVIEWCKILLER INSTINCT GOLDGN64```````
OL,5,BIt's only proper that the Nintendo 64's
OL,6,Bfirst beat 'em up should be a version  
OL,7,Bof Killer Instinct, the game that      
OL,8,Bsupposedly introduced the world to N64 
OL,9,Bin the arcades.                        
OL,11,FAs puffy-jacketed arcade-goers will    
OL,12,Ftestify, the Killer Instinct experience
OL,13,Fis defiantly 2D, albeit with some      
OL,14,Fsplendid 3D backdrops, and superlative 
OL,15,Fpre-rendered sprites.                  
OL,17,BIt's remarkable what Nintendo has      
OL,18,Bmanaged to achieve with this home      
OL,19,Bcartridge version.                     
