OL,3,EPREVIEWCKILLER INSTINCT GOLDGN64```````
OL,5,BOf course, it appears that squeezing   
OL,6,BKiller Instinct's remarkable graphics  
OL,7,Band visual effects onto cartridge      
OL,8,Bhasn't been without it problems.       
OL,10,FSound has suffered. The lo-fi sound    
OL,11,Feffects and musical loops smell bad.   
OL,13,BNintendo has added a host of N64-only  
OL,14,Bfeatures, including six difficulty     
OL,15,Blevels. Also, 10 fighters have made the
OL,16,Btransition from the arcade, with only a
OL,17,Breduced frame rate to show for it.     
OL,19,FIt might be "eggs-actly" what you need!
